            "content_2": "<p>Every flashlight ships in a premium gift box with:</p><p><strong>1×</strong> Ultra Bright LED Flashlight<br><strong>1×</strong> USB-C Charging Cable<br><strong>1×</strong> Carrying Strap Rope<br><strong>1×</strong> Premium Gift Box</p><p>Ready to use or gift out of the box.</p>",
