            "title_4": "Care & Safety",
            "content_4": "<p><strong>Charging:</strong> Use the included USB-C cable. Full charge ~7.5 hours.<br><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep dry when not in use. Charge every 3 months if stored long-term.<br><strong>Safety:</strong> Do not look directly into the beam. Keep away from flammable materials on Strobe mode.<br><strong>Battery:</strong> Lithium battery inside — follow local regulations for air freight.</p>"
